item.description:
Well it's time to start getting outside again. How about coming out and tossing the discs around . We always have a fun time and you don't need to be good at it. Just come and try it. It doesn't cost anything and you'll get some exercise and fresh air.
Bring water, sunscreen , maybe bug spray and your smiles. We will meet at the store and pick up the discs there before heading over to the park.
If people want to eat after, there is a nice sandwich counter we can visit.

if it rains or snows ( heaven forbid ! ) I'll reschedule.

Any questions 603-315-0275
Cindy
item.how_to_find_us: We will meet at the store across from the park to pick up discs
item.name: Wimp Disc Golf
